<inglise> "2. </inglise>
<eesti> "2. </eesti>
<inglise> Sums due under Articles 8, 9, 11 and 16 shall be weighted at a rate fixed on the basis of Articles 64 and 65 (2) of the Staff Regulations for officials of the European Communities, for the country where the recipient of the sum proves he is resident. </inglise>
<eesti> Artiklite 8, 9, 11 ja 16 kohaselt makstavate summade suhtes kohaldatakse selle riigi kohta Euroopa &uuml;henduste ametnike personalieeskirjade artikli 64 ja artikli 65 l&otilde;ike 2 alusel kinnitatud paranduskoefitsienti, kus summa saaja nimetab oma elukoha olevat. </eesti>
<inglise> If the recipient establishes residence in a country for which no weighting has been adopted, the weighting applicable shall be that valid for Belgium. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui saaja nimetab oma elukohana riigi, mille jaoks ei ole paranduskoefitsenti vastu v&otilde;etud, kohaldatakse Belgia suhtes kehtivat paranduskoefitsenti. </eesti>
<inglise> Beneficiaries may elect to be paid, in accordance with the conditions for the payment of remuneration laid down in Article 63 of the abovementioned Staff Regulations, in the currency either of the country of which they are nationals or of their country of residence or of the country where the Court of Auditors is provisionally located; their choice shall remain operative for at least two years. </inglise>
<eesti> Saajad v&otilde;ivad lasta endale eespool nimetatud personalieeskirjade artikliga 63 etten&auml;htud t&ouml;&ouml;tasu maksmise tingimuste kohaselt summad v&auml;lja maksta selle riigi v&auml;&auml;ringus, mille kodanikud nad on, oma asukohariigi v&auml;&auml;ringus v&otilde;i kontrollikoja asukohariigi v&auml;&auml;ringus; valik kehtib v&auml;hemalt kaks aastat. </eesti>
<inglise> Where neither the first nor the second of these countries is a Member State of the Communities the sums due shall be paid in the currency of the country where the Court of Auditors is provisionally located." </inglise>
<eesti> Kui osutatud riikidest esimesed kaks ei ole &uuml;henduste liikmesriigid, makstakse summad v&auml;lja kontrollikoja asukohariigi v&auml;&auml;ringus." </eesti>
